window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>On the first day of their vacation, Sam Archer wakes up to a nightmare. The problem is, he doesn’t sleep. He doesn’t dream. And his nightmare is much more than it seems.</p> <p>For Sam’s entire life, he has been haunted by a man with a grudge against him and his deceased parents. A man who is jealous of his immortality and wishes nothing more than to make Sam’s immortal life as miserable as possible. Thankfully, Sam can't be killed, and he now has the power to defend those he cherishes most.</p> <p>However, even despite his newfound power... His enemy...<i>is going to succeed.</i> Sam has seen it. A future where he loses everyone he loves. Again. And there is absolutely nothing he can do to stop it.</p> <p>His enemy has already guaranteed that, having always been ten steps ahead and having already ensured that it is impossible to overcome this nightmare fate. With no options, and no real hope, outside help slowly starts to trickle into his life. But will it be enough? Sam already knows that the answer is no.</p> <p>But what more can he do, than try anyway? To try as hard as he can to overcome...the impossible.</p> <p><i>The Cosmic Power of an Immortal</i> is a very long full-length novel. It is Book 6 in the Immortal Supers series.</p>"; 
